            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>均華(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6640:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6640\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6640-TW</a>)16日11:57股價下跌125元，報1605.0元，跌幅7.23%，成交785張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>均華(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6640:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6640\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6640-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為機械設備製造業。模具製造業。機械.模具批發業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲18.49%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲5.47%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+61 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-76 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+161 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-24 張</li> <li>融資增減：+129 張</li> <li>融券增減：+2 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
